<li id="c18">
  <div class="cx" id="cx50448806">
   <h5> <a class="de">&nbsp;</a><span class="cu">It is a short-term allocation of labor dollars</span>


<span class="crd ntb">(<a href="/comments/1216271/50448806#c18?mode=alone;showrate=1#c18">4+ / 0-</a>)</span>
  </h5>

  
  


<div class="crs"><dl>
  <dt>Recommended by:</dt><dd>
